                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>50 feet.</p>\n<p>The moonflower releases a pulse of bright light. Each non-moonflower creature in the emanation must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"23\" data-pf2-traits=\"evocation,light,primal,visual\" data-pf2-label=\"Light Pulse DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save.</p>\n<p>The moonflower can't use Light Pulse again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dazzled]{Dazzled} for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Blinded]{Blinded} for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
